  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/946edf843dadfe915f772a5200e0a4e4.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span> <br>\"Oasis\" is a relaxed environmental strategy game, where players transform the barren sandy land into a prosperous and balanced ecosystem by planting various plants, providing living spaces for various organisms, and bringing life back to the dead world.<br><br>You need to plan your money reasonably to purchase the plants and environmental materials needed for sand control. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/405a9810f7c4b968d78190f139342ad8.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Planting plants and arranging environmental materials can bring you income, which can be used to buy more plants and environmental materials. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/3b48bf141b7932b53d6b81b82f891edc.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Planting different types of combinations of plants on a plot can produce different landforms and ecosystems.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/d3485bdb90ce70c08ae65302ec7e5cdd.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/779f223d327cb57b8b499411600c9c38.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>The combination of landforms and ecosystems will attract specific animals to come and live. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/a0f67c7966dc0a0b1c4139437d09d212.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Oasis has a lush hand-drawn pixel environment, pleasant music, and an ambient soundscape filled with atmosphere, giving people a quiet and meditative experience. You can also use the screenshot function to retain your unique sand control results. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/946edf843dadfe915f772a5200e0a4e4.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/946edf843dadfe915f772a5200e0a4e4.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span> <br>\"Oasis\" is a relaxed environmental strategy game, where players transform the barren sandy land into a prosperous and balanced ecosystem by planting various plants, providing living spaces for various organisms, and bringing life back to the dead world.<br><br>You need to plan your money reasonably to purchase the plants and environmental materials needed for sand control. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/405a9810f7c4b968d78190f139342ad8.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Planting plants and arranging environmental materials can bring you income, which can be used to buy more plants and environmental materials. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/3b48bf141b7932b53d6b81b82f891edc.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Planting different types of combinations of plants on a plot can produce different landforms and ecosystems.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/d3485bdb90ce70c08ae65302ec7e5cdd.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/779f223d327cb57b8b499411600c9c38.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>The combination of landforms and ecosystems will attract specific animals to come and live. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/a0f67c7966dc0a0b1c4139437d09d212.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Oasis has a lush hand-drawn pixel environment, pleasant music, and an ambient soundscape filled with atmosphere, giving people a quiet and meditative experience. You can also use the screenshot function to retain your unique sand control results. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/946edf843dadfe915f772a5200e0a4e4.avif?t=1732440609\" width=480 height=270 /></span>",
